OL,3,CMan who sexually assaulted woman as
OL,4,Cshe slept in hotel jailed
OL,6,FA Somerset man who sexually assaulted
OL,7,Fa woman while she was asleep has been
OL,8,Fjailed.
OL,10,FDavid Braun, 53, from Taunton,
OL,11,Fattacked the woman at a hotel in the
OL,12,FForest of Dean two years ago.
OL,14,FThe victim, who says her world has
OL,15,Fbeen 'torn apart' by the attack, woke
OL,16,Fup during the assault.
OL,18,FBraun was arrested, charged and
OL,19,Feventually found guilty on 6 June for
OL,20,Fthe offence following a trial at
OL,21,FGloucester Crown Court.
