OL,3,CMan who sexually assaulted woman as
OL,4,Cshe slept in hotel jailed
OL,6,FDetective Constable Tom Newrick from
OL,7,FGloucestershire Police said: "Braun
OL,8,Fviolated the victim when she was at
OL,9,Fher most vulnerable" and described his
OL,10,Factions as "appalling".
OL,12,F"The victim has been extremely brave
OL,13,Fthroughout our investigation, working
OL,14,Fwith us and giving evidence in court",
OL,15,Fhe said.
OL,17,F"I hope this outcome shows that cases
OL,18,Fof this nature will be dealt with
OL,19,Frobustly and with the utmost
OL,20,Fseriousness."
