OL,6,FCPS South West District Crown
OL,7,FProsecutor Jill Macnamara said: "We
OL,8,Fwant every victim of sexual assault to
OL,9,Fhave the confidence to come forward to
OL,10,Freport abuse, in the knowledge that
OL,11,Fsupport is available and that the
OL,12,Fpolice and Crown Prosecution Service
OL,13,Fare committed to securing justice."
OL,15,FThe Judge said he had read statements
OL,16,Fwhich had been provided about Braun's
OL,17,Fcharacter and that he would take
OL,18,Fmitigating factors into account when
OL,19,Fsentencing.
